{"tid":668094,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"劉馬車就放監，出返黎會唔會報仇呢？","createTime":"2018-05-17T10:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-17T10:48:52.000Z","uid":122522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cbbed6f18644d20bd56c76928f0bdf122c8fb621","tid":668094,"uid":122522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:12:31.000Z","msg":"劉馬車（英語：Carriage Lau ，真名劉駿軒，1996年4月15日－），香港網絡紅人、演員，曾活躍於YouTube，並以「全港最高質YouTuber」自居，截至2015年9月1日，其訂閱人數達4萬人，但其後有所回落。2016年9月，「劉馬車」在因犯強制猥褻罪和猥褻兒童罪，被深圳市福田區人民法院判處有期徒刑兩年六個月。"},{"pid":"8baa14383219652d874ceb1fbefb5eec2629bbaa","tid":668094,"uid":142128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:13:44.000Z","msg":"食屎狗"},{"pid":"fe647bafade667581e478c7bbcb8c4f917285164","tid":668094,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:15:12.000Z","msg":"coffee lam"},{"pid":"ab708fa0f79be289bc44d03d47ae170a686e6598","tid":668094,"uid":19920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:18:55.000Z","msg":"幾時會再出片"},{"pid":"6b55f215ae0b4b773e4559b188cc79adaf06b4be","tid":668094,"uid":148056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:22:15.000Z","msg":"菜刀玩屎眼"},{"pid":"19ec8e9564beaa0ce6e442c620bd8f9a6315f588","tid":668094,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:25:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f6119372f6bb8607ca41e3cc0da2c58de1a9eb1b","tid":668094,"uid":48905,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/17/184849_e497ee2eb3a0ad4354db91e03602c32f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F17%2F184849_e497ee2eb3a0ad4354db91e03602c32f.png&h=4830c316&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}